Hexagram: 2 - ไท - K'un
Locus:
  Description: Judgement
Title: Receptive Service
---
The mare is commended as the model of docility and strength. The role of the
subject is one of unhesitating response and cheerful service to mankind. He
requires friends during hours of work but should be alone with his chief
when receiving instructions and reporting achievements.
